<concept id="CreativeAutoShooting-B10294BA" xml:lang="en">
<title>Creative Auto Shooting</title>
<shortdesc>The Creative Auto (CA) mode enables you to exercise more
control over the decisions the camera makes when shooting in Intelligent
Auto.</shortdesc>
<prolog>
<metadata><keywords><indexterm>Creative Auto</indexterm></keywords>
</metadata>
</prolog>
<conbody>
<p>In the CA mode you can easily change the depth of field and drive
mode. You can also choose the a ambience you want to convey in your
images. The default settings are the same as the Intelligent Auto
mode.<fn>Refer to the section on Intelligent Auto mode for default
settings.</fn></p><?Pub Caret 273?>
</conbody>
</concept>
